#: ../../F/followup.rst:5
msgid "followup"
msgstr "followup"

#: ../../F/followup.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../F/followup.rst:9
msgid ""
"[common] On Usenet, a :ref:`posting` generated in response to another "
"posting (as opposed to a :ref:`reply`\\, which goes by email rather than "
"being broadcast). Followups include the ID of the :ref:`parent-message` in "
"their headers; smart news-readers can use this information to present Usenet"
" news in ‘conversation’ sequence rather than order-of-arrival. See "
":ref:`thread`\\."
msgstr ""
"[一般的]Usenetで、別の投稿への応答として生成される\\ :ref:`posting`\\ (ブロードキャストされるのではなくメールで送られる\\"
" :ref:`reply`\\ とは対照的)。followupはヘッダーに\\ :ref:`parent-message`\\ "
"のIDを含む。賢いニュースリーダーはこの情報を使って、Usenetニュースを到着順ではなく‘会話’の順序で提示できる。\\ "
":ref:`thread`\\ を参照。"
